---
title: Paprika Chicken & Broccoli with Rustic Herb Potato Wedges
description: Our paprika chicken is a take on the Hungarian national dish, ‘chicken paprikash’, and is made with ample amounts of delicious sweet paprika. And the best thing… the creamy sauce is made in the same pan to give you a super flavoursome result!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/paprika-chicken-broccoli-cd6c458e.jpg
